  "_meta": {
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "created": "2026-04-19",
    "notes": [
      "Maps US states + DC + territories + CA provinces to optimal VN send hour.",
      "Optimal = email lands when recipient is starting their workday (9-11h local).",
      "VN is UTC+7. offset_from_utc is standard time offset (no DST adjustment).",
      "optimal_send_hour_vn uses 24h format (0-23). Send 1h BEFORE target local arrival.",
      "Most US states observe DST (spring forward 1h Mar-Nov). Adjust mentally during summer.",
      "Alaska DST: UTC-8 standard / UTC-9 no-DST. Hawaii: no DST ever (UTC-10 always)."
    ]
  },
